= Upgrade steps =

* (For the sensible) backup all Movable Type files and the database
* Connect to <tt>mt-check.cgi</tt> to ensure that minimum Perl version (5.6.1) requirement is met
* Upload new files
* Hit <tt>mt-upgrade.cgi</tt>
* Delete  <tt>mt-upgrade.cgi</tt>
